"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![DefiCalendar](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*qLFUbB9JSrMQY-mwpVNNRw.jpeg)\\n\\n\\\\*Follow us to receive the latest airdrop and whitelist updates.Twitter: *<https://twitter.com/CalendarDefi>*Medium: *<https://medium.com/@CalendarDefi>*.Telegram channel: \\\\**<https://t.me/deficalendar>*\\n\\nWe continue with projects that have not yet launched their tokens. We covered [DEX aggregators](https://medium.com/@CalendarDefi/airdrop-whitelist-complete-guide-the-dex-aggregator-series-a6b160cb1741) and [cross-chain bridges](https://medium.com/@CalendarDefi/airdrop-whitelist-complete-guide-the-bridges-series-5531b1fffad0) before. We focus on borrowing aggregators this time. Borrowing aggregators get you the cheapest loan by always borrowing from the base protocol (Compound, Aave, etc…) proposing the best rate.\\n\\n**FujiDAO**\\n\\n<https://app.fujidao.org/> (ETH Mainnet)\\n\\n<https://fantom.fujidao.org/> (Fantom)\\n\\nFuji DAO is the first borrowing aggregator. They are currently on ETH mainnet as well as Fantom.\\n\\nThe first NFT [drop](https://medium.com/fuji-finance/releasing-fujiflops-nft-f6d35540cf9f) to their OG is now over but the team has said there is more to come later. Keep track of their [Twitter](https://twitter.com/FujiFinance) and [Discord](https://t.co/HFwBQU5KHg?amp=1) if you are interested.\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*QfFTFrQEcUS2nJlv)\\n\\nTo pay lower gas costs, you can interact with the protocol at Fantom. Right now the only pairs available are FTM/DAI, FTM/USDC and BTC/DAI. The liquidity is sourced from Geist, Scream and IronBank.\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*IlMr9Byw2TuMPOnM9ZiDwA.png)\\n\\n**Greenwood**\\n\\n[https://router.greenwood.finance/](https://router.greenwood.finance/)\\n\\nAnother borrowing aggregator on ETH mainnet and Arbitrum. No confirmation of airdrops from the team.\\n\\nInteract on Arbitrum to save gas costs. Provide your feedback [here](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSckRSeqeCQFg2td5fO1pU4kT0gi459oic9Zp_7KwB347b6H7A/viewform) to help the team.\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*qSW-w6124uoPIDfNVhidxw.png)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1637314125,\"title\":\"Airdrop/Whitelist Complete Guide — The Borrowing Aggregator Series\"},\"digest\":\"oMgR4wjTwuuH1O5UKvUCrfv5OV6Dy94aaOaB3cSs4mQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xbd52c13827f012797005F57E4dB3b8db155580F2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"bREx2AmoKJEHOdZ_4-r-fJ3Q17ns774ZzbQ1ljGUH-A\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"CwjhI9YFyPFcMdx3UwGOrz9kY1VkE1DlLwHKOlea4dU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ujbGJMI_w5WbGkwreuZCJmooA2RIIwYqLentaM3ECJgL1TswIt2JdKldm4u6s-Q4jFeGmnsUZzBUjR3n4iEx7w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x61b5df9f5433ba81fab634729ad9d2a331f6b5bbe114cd5039467fab9bdbeaae30183ec461de8c86dc6e87046c04c67f1193ce60882c8b30c80a0191347bd64f1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"bREx2AmoKJEHOdZ_4-r-fJ3Q17ns774ZzbQ1ljGUH-A\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"CwjhI9YFyPFcMdx3UwGOrz9kY1VkE1DlLwHKOlea4dU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"oMgR4wjTwuuH1O5UKvUCrfv5OV6Dy94aaOaB3cSs4mQ\"}"